Rolls Royce May Sell Tidal Power Turbines by 2015, Times Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-04-10T13:08:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/rolls-royce-may-sell-tidal-power-turbines-by-2015-times-says.html
Rolls Royce Group Plc could be
selling turbines for use in tidal power generation projects by
2015, the  Sunday Times  reported, citing unidentified people in
the industry.  The company plans to install a prototype turbine in the
Pentland Firth in northeast  Scotland  next year, replacing a
smaller device already at the site, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London at 
 rgraham13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
